code: private void maybePause(int bytes) throws IOException {     bytesSinceLastRateLimit += bytes.     if (bytesSinceLastRateLimit >= rateLimiter.getMinPauseCheckBytes()) {         long pause = rateLimiter.pause(bytesSinceLastRateLimit).         bytesSinceLastRateLimit = 0.         if (pause > 0) {             listener.onPause(pause).         }     } }
@Override public int read() throws IOException {     int b = super.read().     maybePause(1).     return b. }
@Override public int read(byte[] b, int off, int len) throws IOException {     int n = super.read(b, off, len).     if (n > 0) {         maybePause(n).     }     return n. }
